labels.label:
Note: All observed lightning strikes are in the 
siemens observation table
--> set lightning to false wherever it is not true after 
the lightning data import
Meteostat - insert complete record if visual crossing record is missing (no data for Gwynt-y-Mor --> ignore location)
Get missing Visual Crossing field values from Meteostat --> select records with missing field values from weather_data

Note: Merge the offshore location data before 
importing lightning data (lightning data will be 
updated for the merged locations)
--> process group "Offshore Data Merge" on the 
main screen

properties.Text:
SELECT observation_date, observation_time, location_name, ${field_name}
FROM weather_data_meteostat
WHERE observation_date = '${observation_date}'
AND observation_time = '${observation_time}'
AND location_name = '${location_name}'

UPDATE weather_data 
SET ${field_name} = '${${field_name}:replaceNull('NULL')}'
WHERE observation_date = '${observation_date}'
AND observation_time = '${observation_time}' 
AND location_name = '${location_name}'

UPDATE weather_data 
SET lightning = 'True'
WHERE observation_date = '${observation_date}'
AND extract(hour from observation_time) = extract(hour from '${observation_time}'::time)
AND location_name = '${location_name}'

INSERT INTO weather_data (
	observation_date, 
	observation_time, 
	location_name, 
	technology, 
	longitude, 
	latitude, 
	snow,
	ice,
	temperature_c, 
	windspeed_m_s, 
	windgusts_m_s, 
	visibility_km, 
	original_source)
VALUES (
	'${observation_date}'
	,'${observation_time}' 
	,'${location_name}'
	,'${technology}'
	,${longitude:replaceNull('NULL')}
	,${latitude:replaceNull('NULL')} 
	,'${snow:replaceNull('NULL')}'
	,'${ice:replaceNull('NULL')}'  
	,${temperature_c:replaceNull('NULL')}
	,${windspeed_m_s:replaceNull('NULL')}
	,${windgusts_m_s:replaceNull('NULL')} 
	,${visibility_km:replaceNull('NULL')} 
	,'Visual Crossing'	
)
ON CONFLICT ON CONSTRAINT unique_timestamp_and_location DO UPDATE
SET snow = '${snow:replaceNull('NULL')}', 
	ice = '${ice:replaceNull('NULL')}', 
	temperature_c = ${temperature_c:replaceNull('NULL')}, 
	windspeed_m_s = ${windspeed_m_s:replaceNull('NULL')}, 
	windgusts_m_s = ${windgusts_m_s:replaceNull('NULL')}, 
	visibility_km = ${visibility_km:replaceNull('NULL')}, 
	original_source = 'Visual Crossing'

UPDATE weather_data 
SET ${field_name} = ${${field_name}:replaceNull('NULL')}
WHERE observation_date = '${observation_date}'
AND observation_time = '${observation_time}' 
AND location_name = '${location_name}'

INSERT INTO weather_data (
	observation_date, 
	observation_time, 
	location_name, 
	technology, 
	longitude, 
	latitude, 
	snow,
	ice,
	temperature_c, 
	windspeed_m_s, 
	windgusts_m_s, 
	visibility_km, 
	original_source)
VALUES (
	'${observation_date}'
	,'${observation_time}' 
	,'${location_name}'
	,'${technology}'
	,${longitude:replaceNull('NULL')}
	,${latitude:replaceNull('NULL')} 
	,'${snow:replaceNull('NULL')}'
	,'${ice:replaceNull('NULL')}'  
	,${temperature_c:replaceNull('NULL')}
	,${windspeed_m_s:replaceNull('NULL')}
	,${windgusts_m_s:replaceNull('NULL')} 
	,${visibility_km:replaceNull('NULL')} 
	,'Meteostat'	
)
ON CONFLICT ON CONSTRAINT unique_timestamp_and_location DO NOTHING
